AI-Driven Intelligent EV Charging Station Recommender with Generative AI-based Conversational Assistant for Shell

EV owners often face challenges in finding the optimal charging station considering convenience, queue status, price, vehicle needs, and infrastructure reliability. The project aims to develop an intelligent system that predicts and recommends the best Shell charging stations for users in real-time. The solution will also feature a generative AI-powered chatbot to help users with natural language queries about charging options, scheduling, pricing, and trip planning, thereby improving user experience and Shellâ€™s operational efficiency.

Data set https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/vivekattri/global-ev-charging-stations-dataset

